      <title>01_10x程序员是如何思考的？</title>
      <link>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/10x%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E6%B3%95/01_10x%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%91%98%E6%98%AF%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E7%9A%84/</link>
